        crm:P2_has_type          <urn:uuid:a6e0d285-571b-4359-8c63-ebd8317cc4b3> ;
        crm:P3_has_note          "3D web viewer and dashboard designed as a collaborative platform for RHDT visualisation, data interaction and knowledge creation. Provides access to linked data through multiple layers of information, enriching 3D digital replicas of CH assets. Enables access to instrumented area mappings and associated IoT stream data via dedicated dashboard, displaying data and simulation results from ARTEMIS simulation services. Based on Xeokit, Potree/Cesium js stacks." ;
